### Login
POST http://localhost:4000/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@acme.local",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Get Approval Detail
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/approvals/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### View Document PDF
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/documents/3/view
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get Document Approval History
GET http://localhost:4000/api/v1/approvals/document/3
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
